lead_paragraph: A rare weekday game under a hot sun at Dodger Stadium dragged into rush hour with the Baltimore Orioles and Los Angeles Dodgers blowing numerous scoring chances.

headline.print_headline: Orioles Outlast Dodgers 6-4 in 14 Innings in 36K Game
